# TextField (Text Field_v2)

Shared floating-label input at `src/app/components/TextField.tsx`. **This is the only text/input field in the UMP component library.** All form text inputs, password fields, email fields, URL fields, date fields, and textareas MUST use this component.

## When to Use
- Login forms (email, password with eye toggle via `trailingIcon`)
- Payment Pages forms (page info, settings, property panels)
- Popup form fields (via `PopupInput` which wraps `TextField`)
- Any form collecting text input

## When NOT to Use
- Search bars (Header, SearchWithDropdown) — standalone pill-shaped components
- Checkboxes, toggles, radio buttons
- File upload inputs
- Select/dropdown menus
- Inline row inputs (e.g., option items in PropertyPanel) — use plain `<input>`

## Container
- Height: 56px (`size="default"`), 44px (`size="compact"`)
- **Same height in all states** (idle, focus, filled)
- Border radius: `rounded-[4px]`
- Border: 1px `#e0e0e0` (Normal/Filled), `#004299` (Hover/Focus), `#fd5154` (Error)
- Background: `bg-white` (Normal), `bg-[#ebebeb]` (Disabled)
- Padding: **16px** left/right (`px-[16px]`), **8px** top/bottom (`py-[8px]`)

## Internal Layout (Filled/Focus)
- Label height: **16px** (`leading-[16px]`)
- Input value height: **24px** (`leading-[24px]`)
- Math: 8px top + 16px label + 24px value + 8px bottom = **56px**

## Floating Label States
| State | Label | Border | Background |
|---|---|---|---|
| Normal (empty) | centered, `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#7e7e7e]` | `#e0e0e0` | white |
| Hover | same | `#004299` | white |
| Focus (empty) | floats top-left, `text-[12px] font-normal text-[#7e7e7e]` | `#004299` | white |
| Focus Filled | floated, input visible | `#004299` | white |
| Filled (unfocused) | floated, input visible | `#e0e0e0` | white |
| Disabled | `text-[#acacac]` | — | `#ebebeb` |

## Variants
- **Error**: border `#fd5154`, assistive text `text-[12px] text-[#fd5154]`
- **Assistive text**: `text-[12px] text-[#101010]`
- **Prefix**: left-aligned in `bg-[#fafafa]` with `border-r`
- **Trailing icon**: right-aligned slot (e.g., Eye toggle)
- **`type="date"`**: native calendar glyph hidden; **`CalenderOutlinedIcon`** from `Icons.tsx` (**24×24px**, `size-[24px]`, `text-[#7e7e7e]` → hover `text-[#101010]`) in a button with `aria-label="Open calendar"`; opens picker via `showPicker()` / `click()`. Override with explicit `trailingIcon` if needed.
- **Multiline**: textarea mode with `rows` prop
- **Compact**: `size="compact"` — 44px, `text-[13px]`

## Autofill Detection
Uses `onAnimationStart` + CSS `@keyframes onAutoFillStart` / `onAutoFillCancel` to detect Chrome autofill and float label correctly. Keyframes in `theme.css`.

## Props
```tsx
interface TextFieldProps {
  label: string;
  value: string;
  onChange: (value: string) => void;
  type?: "text" | "email" | "url" | "number" | "password" | "date";
  disabled?: boolean;
  error?: string;
  assistiveText?: string;
  required?: boolean;
  prefix?: string;
  trailingIcon?: React.ReactNode;
  multiline?: boolean;
  rows?: number;
  size?: "default" | "compact";
}
```

## Usage
- **LoginPage**: `<TextField label="Mobile Number or Email" />`, `<TextField label="Paytm Password" type="password" trailingIcon={<Eye/>} />`
- **PageInfoForm**: Form Name, URL Path (prefix), HTML Title, etc.
- **AdditionalSettings**: Redirect URL, Success Message (multiline)
- **PropertyPanel**: Compact variant for component properties
- **PopupInput**: Wraps `TextField` for popup contexts
